  "text": "The association of colony macrophages with capillaries was clearly noted in matrigel assays. Macrophages isolated from the cocultures were coinjected with IMECs in matrigel plugs. After 7 days, vascular networks were found highly decorated with macrophages ( Figure 6F ) simulating the intimate interaction between macrophages and blood vessels described in vivo. [CITATION_1] ",
